#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:9
msgid "Uptime below one day"
msgstr "ເວລາເຮັດວຽກຂອງລະບົບ (Uptime) ໜ້ອຍກວ່າໜຶ່ງວັນ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:12
msgid "Uptime is less than 1 day, performance tuning may not be accurate."
msgstr "ເວລາເຮັດວຽກຂອງລະບົບໜ້ອຍກວ່າ 1 ວັນ, ການປັບແຕ່ງປະສິດທິພາບອາດຈະບໍ່ຊັດເຈນ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:14
msgid ""
"To have more accurate averages it is recommended to let the server run for "
"longer than a day before running this analyzer"
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອໃຫ້ໄດ້ຄ່າສະເລ່ຍທີ່ຊັດເຈນກວ່າ, ແນະນຳໃຫ້ປ່ອຍໃຫ້ເຊີເວີເຮັດວຽກດົນກວ່າໜຶ່ງວັນກ່ອນທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ຕົວວິເຄາະນີ້"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:17
#, possible-php-format
msgid "The uptime is only %s"
msgstr "ເວລາເຮັດວຽກຂອງລະບົບແມ່ນພຽງແຕ່ %s"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:22
msgid "Questions below 1,000"
msgstr "ຄຳຖາມ (Questions) ຕ່ຳກວ່າ 1,000"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:26
msgid ""
"Fewer than 1,000 questions have been run against this server. The "
"recommendations may not be accurate."
msgstr ""
"ມີຄຳຖາມໜ້ອຍກວ່າ 1,000 ຄຳຖາມທີ່ຖືກສົ່ງມາຫາເຊີເວີນີ້. ຄຳແນະນຳອາດຈະບໍ່ຊັດເຈນ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:30
msgid ""
"Let the server run for a longer time until it has executed a greater amount "
"of queries."
msgstr ""
"ປ່ອຍໃຫ້ເຊີເວີເຮັດວຽກດົນກວ່າເກົ່າ ຈົນກວ່າມັນຈະປະມວນຜົນຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມໄດ້ໃນຈຳນວນທີ່ຫຼາຍຂຶ້ນ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:32
#, possible-php-format
msgid "Current amount of Questions: %s"
msgstr "ຈຳນວນຄຳຖາມໃນປັດຈຸບັນ: %s"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:37
msgid "Percentage of slow queries"
msgstr "ເປີເຊັນຂອງຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມທີ່ຊ້າ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:41
msgid ""
"There is a lot of slow queries compared to the overall amount of Queries."
msgstr "ມີຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມທີ່ຊ້າເປັນຈຳນວນຫຼາຍ ເມື່ອທຽບກັບຈຳນວນຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມທັງໝົດ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:43
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:57
msgid ""
"You might want to increase {long_query_time} or optimize the queries listed "
"in the slow query log"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານອາດຈະຕ້ອງການເພີ່ມຄ່າ {long_query_time} ຫຼື ປັບແຕ່ງຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນລັອກຄຳສັ່ງທີ່ຊ້າ (slow "
"query log)"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:46
#, possible-php-format
msgid "The slow query rate should be below 5%%, your value is %s%%."
msgstr "ອັດຕາຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມທີ່ຊ້າຄວນຕ່ຳກວ່າ 5%%, ຄ່າຂອງທ່ານແມ່ນ %s%%."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:51
msgid "Slow query rate"
msgstr "ອັດຕາຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມທີ່ຊ້າ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:55
msgid ""
"There is a high percentage of slow queries compared to the server uptime."
msgstr "ມີເປີເຊັນຂອງຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມທີ່ຊ້າສູງ ເມື່ອທຽບກັບເວລາເຮັດວຽກຂອງເຊີເວີ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:60
#, possible-php-format
msgid ""
"You have a slow query rate of %s per hour, you should have less than 1%% per "
"hour."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານມີອັດຕາຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມທີ່ຊ້າ %s ຕໍ່ຊົ່ວໂມງ, ທ່ານຄວນມີຕ່ຳກວ່າ 1%% ຕໍ່ຊົ່ວໂມງ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:65
msgid "Long query time"
msgstr "ເວລາຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມທີ່ດົນ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:69
msgid ""
"{long_query_time} is set to 10 seconds or more, thus only slow queries that "
"take above 10 seconds are logged."
msgstr ""
"{long_query_time} ຖືກຕັ້ງໄວ້ທີ່ 10 ວິນາທີ ຫຼື ຫຼາຍກວ່າ, ດັ່ງນັ້ນສະເພາະຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມທີ່ຊ້າກວ່າ 10 ວິນາ"
"ທີ ຈຶ່ງຈະຖືກບັນທຶກລັອກ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:73
msgid ""
"It is suggested to set {long_query_time} to a lower value, depending on your "
"environment. Usually a value of 1-5 seconds is suggested."
msgstr ""
"ແນະນຳໃຫ້ຕັ້ງຄ່າ {long_query_time} ໃຫ້ຕ່ຳລົງ, ຂຶ້ນກັບສະພາບແວດລ້ອມການໃຊ້ງານຂອງທ່ານ. ໂດຍທົ່ວໄປແ"
"ລ້ວແນະນຳໃຫ້ຕັ້ງເປັນ 1-5 ວິນາທີ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:76
#, possible-php-format
msgid "long_query_time is currently set to %ds."
msgstr "long_query_time ຖືກຕັ້ງໄວ້ທີ່ %ds ໃນປັດຈຸບັນ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:81
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:94
msgid "Slow query logging"
msgstr "ການບັນທຶກລັອກຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມທີ່ຊ້າ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:85
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:98
msgid "The slow query log is disabled."
msgstr "ການບັນທຶກລັອກຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມທີ່ຊ້າຖືກປິດໃຊ້ງານຢູ່."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:87
msgid ""
"Enable slow query logging by setting {log_slow_queries} to 'ON'. This will "
"help troubleshooting badly performing queries."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດໃຊ້ການບັນທຶກລັອກຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມທີ່ຊ້າໂດຍການຕັ້ງຄ່າ {log_slow_queries} ເປັນ 'ON'. ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະຊ່ວຍໃ"
"ນການແກ້ໄຂບັນຫາຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມທີ່ມີປະສິດທິພາບຕ່ຳ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:90
msgid "log_slow_queries is set to 'OFF'"
msgstr "log_slow_queries ຖືກຕັ້ງເປັນ 'OFF'"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:100
msgid ""
"Enable slow query logging by setting {slow_query_log} to 'ON'. This will "
"help troubleshooting badly performing queries."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດໃຊ້ການບັນທຶກລັອກຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມທີ່ຊ້າໂດຍການຕັ້ງຄ່າ {slow_query_log} ເປັນ 'ON'. ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະຊ່ວຍໃນກ"
"ານແກ້ໄຂບັນຫາຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມທີ່ມີປະສິດທິພາບຕ່ຳ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:103
msgid "slow_query_log is set to 'OFF'"
msgstr "slow_query_log ຖືກຕັ້ງເປັນ 'OFF'"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:108
msgid "Release Series"
msgstr "Release Series"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:111
msgid "The MySQL server version less than 5.1."
msgstr "ເວີຊັນຂອງເຊີເວີ MySQL ຕ່ຳກວ່າ 5.1."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:113
msgid ""
"You should upgrade, as MySQL 5.1 has improved performance, and MySQL 5.5 "
"even more so."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຄວນອັບເກຣດ, ເພາະວ່າ MySQL 5.1 ໄດ້ປັບປຸງປະສິດທິພາບດີຂຶ້ນ ແລະ MySQL 5.5 ກໍຍິ່ງດີກວ່າເກົ່າ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:115
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:129
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:140
#, possible-php-format
msgid "Current version: %s"
msgstr "ເວີຊັນປັດຈຸບັນ: %s"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:120
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:134
msgid "Minor Version"
msgstr "ເວີຊັນຍ່ອຍ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:124
msgid "Version less than 5.1.30 (the first GA release of 5.1)."
msgstr "ເວີຊັນຕ່ຳກວ່າ 5.1.30 (ລຸ້ນ GA ທຳອິດຂອງ 5.1)."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:126
msgid ""
"You should upgrade, as recent versions of MySQL 5.1 have improved "
"performance and MySQL 5.5 even more so."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຄວນອັບເກຣດ, ເພາະວ່າ MySQL 5.1 ເວີຊັນຫຼ້າສຸດໄດ້ປັບປຸງປະສິດທິພາບດີຂຶ້ນ ແລະ MySQL 5.5 ກໍຍິ່ງດີກວ່"
"າເກົ່າ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:138
msgid "Version less than 5.5.8 (the first GA release of 5.5)."
msgstr "ເວີຊັນຕ່ຳກວ່າ 5.5.8 (ລຸ້ນ GA ທຳອິດຂອງ 5.5)."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:139
msgid "You should upgrade, to a stable version of MySQL 5.5."
msgstr "ທ່ານຄວນອັບເກຣດເປັນ MySQL 5.5 ເວີຊັນທີ່ມີຄວາມສະຖຽນ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:145
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:158
msgid "Distribution"
msgstr "ການແຈກຢາຍ (Distribution)"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:148
msgid "Version is compiled from source, not a MySQL official binary."
msgstr ""
"ເວີຊັນນີ້ຖືກຄອມໄພລ໌ (compile) ຈາກຊອສໂຄດ, ບໍ່ແມ່ນໄຟລ໌ບາຍນາຣີທາງການຂອງ MySQL."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:150
msgid ""
"If you did not compile from source, you may be using a package modified by a "
"distribution. The MySQL manual only is accurate for official MySQL binaries, "
"not any package distributions (such as RedHat, Debian/Ubuntu etc)."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າທ່ານບໍ່ໄດ້ຄອມໄພລ໌ຈາກຊອສໂຄດ, ທ່ານອາດຈະໃຊ້ແພັກເກດທີ່ຖືກດັດແປງໂດຍຜູ້ແຈກຢາຍ. ຄູ່ມື MySQL ຈະຖືກຕ້ອງ"
"ສະເພາະກັບໄຟລ໌ບາຍນາຣີທາງການຂອງ MySQL ເທົ່ານັ້ນ, ບໍ່ແມ່ນແພັກເກດຈາກຜູ້ແຈກຢາຍອື່ນໆ (ເຊັ່ນ RedHat, "
"Debian/Ubuntu ແລະ ອື່ນໆ)."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:154
msgid "'source' found in version_comment"
msgstr "ພົບ 'source' ໃນ version_comment"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:161
msgid "The MySQL manual only is accurate for official MySQL binaries."
msgstr "ຄູ່ມື MySQL ຈະຖືກຕ້ອງສະເພາະກັບໄຟລ໌ບາຍນາຣີທາງການຂອງ MySQL ເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:163
msgid ""
"Percona documentation is at <a href=\"https://www.percona.com/software/"
"documentation/\">https://www.percona.com/software/documentation/</a>"
msgstr ""
"ເອກະສານຂອງ Percona ຢູ່ທີ່ <a href=\"https://www.percona.com/software/"
"documentation/\">https://www.percona.com/software/documentation/</a>"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:166
msgid "'percona' found in version_comment"
msgstr "ພົບ 'percona' ໃນ version_comment"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:170
msgid "MySQL Architecture"
msgstr "ສະຖາປັດຕະຍະກຳ MySQL"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:174
msgid "MySQL is not compiled as a 64-bit package."
msgstr "MySQL ບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກຄອມໄພລ໌ເປັນແພັກເກດ 64 ບິດ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:176
msgid ""
"Your memory capacity is above 3 GiB (assuming the Server is on localhost), "
"so MySQL might not be able to access all of your memory. You might want to "
"consider installing the 64-bit version of MySQL."
msgstr ""
"ຄວາມຈຳ (RAM) ຂອງທ່ານຫຼາຍກວ່າ 3 GiB (ສົມມຸດວ່າເຊີເວີຢູ່ localhost), ດັ່ງນັ້ນ MySQL ອາດຈະບໍ່ສາມ"
"າດເຂົ້າເຖິງຄວາມຈຳທັງໝົດຂອງທ່ານໄດ້. ທ່ານອາດຈະພິຈາລະນາຕິດຕັ້ງ MySQL ເວີຊັນ 64 ບິດ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:180
#, possible-php-format
msgid "Available memory on this host: %s"
msgstr "ຄວາມຈຳທີ່ມີໃຫ້ໃນໂຮສນີ້: %s"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:186
msgid "Query caching method"
msgstr "ວິທີການເຮັດແຄຊຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:190
msgid "Suboptimal caching method."
msgstr "ວິທີການເຮັດແຄຊຍັງບໍ່ດີເທົ່າທີ່ຄວນ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:192
msgid ""
"You are using the MySQL Query cache with a fairly high traffic database. It "
"might be worth considering to use <a href=\"https://dev.mysql.com/doc/"
"refman/5.6/en/ha-memcached.html\">memcached</a> instead of the MySQL Query "
"cache, especially if you have multiple slaves."
msgstr ""
"ເຈົ້າກຳລັງໃຊ້ MySQL Query cache ກັບຖານຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ມີທຣາຟຟິກຂ້ອນຂ້າງສູງ. ເຈົ້າອາດຈະພິຈາລະນາໃຊ້ <a "
"href=\"https://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/5.6/en/ha-memcached.html\">"
"memcached</a> ແທນ MySQL Query cache, ໂດຍສະເພາະຖ້າເຈົ້າມີເຊີເວີລູກ (Slaves) ຫຼາຍໂຕ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:198
#, possible-php-format
msgid ""
"The query cache is enabled and the server receives %d queries per second. "
"This rule fires if there is more than 100 queries per second."
msgstr ""
"Query cache ຖືກເປີດໃຊ້ງານ ແລະ ເຊີເວີໄດ້ຮັບ %d ຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມຕໍ່ວິນາທີ. ກົດເກນນີ້ຈະເຮັດວຽກຖ້າມີຫຼາຍກ"
"ວ່າ 100 ຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມຕໍ່ວິນາທີ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:206
msgid "Percentage of sorts that cause temporary tables"
msgstr "ເປີເຊັນຂອງການຈັດລຽງທີ່ເຮັດໃຫ້ເກີດຕາຕະລາງຊົ່ວຄາວ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:210
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:223
msgid "Too many sorts are causing temporary tables."
msgstr "ການຈັດລຽງຫຼາຍເກີນໄປກຳລັງເຮັດໃຫ້ເກີດຕາຕະລາງຊົ່ວຄາວ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:212
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:225
msgid ""
"Consider increasing {sort_buffer_size} and/or {read_rnd_buffer_size}, "
"depending on your system memory limits."
msgstr ""
"ພິຈາລະນາເພີ່ມ {sort_buffer_size} ແລະ/ຫຼື {read_rnd_buffer_size}, ໂດຍຂຶ້ນກັບຂີດຈຳກັດຄວາມ"
"ຈຳຂອງລະບົບຂອງທ່ານ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:215
#, possible-php-format
msgid ""
"%s%% of all sorts cause temporary tables, this value should be lower than "
"10%%."
msgstr ""
"%s%% ຂອງການຈັດລຽງທັງໝົດເຮັດໃຫ້ເກີດຕາຕະລາງຊົ່ວຄາວ, ຄ່ານີ້ຄວນຕ່ຳກວ່າ 10%%."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:220
msgid "Rate of sorts that cause temporary tables"
msgstr "ອັດຕາການຈັດລຽງທີ່ເຮັດໃຫ້ເກີດຕາຕະລາງຊົ່ວຄາວ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:228
#, possible-php-format
msgid ""
"Temporary tables average: %s, this value should be less than 1 per hour."
msgstr "ຄ່າສະເລ່ຍຂອງຕາຕະລາງຊົ່ວຄາວ: %s, ຄ່ານີ້ຄວນຕ່ຳກວ່າ 1 ຕໍ່ຊົ່ວໂມງ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:233
msgid "Sort rows"
msgstr "ຈັດລຽງແຖວ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:236
msgid "There are lots of rows being sorted."
msgstr "ມີແຖວຈຳນວນຫຼາຍກຳລັງຖືກຈັດລຽງ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:238
msgid ""
"While there is nothing wrong with a high amount of row sorting, you might "
"want to make sure that the queries which require a lot of sorting use "
"indexed columns in the ORDER BY clause, as this will result in much faster "
"sorting."
msgstr ""
"ເຖິງວ່າຈະບໍ່ມີຫຍັງຜິດປົກກະຕິກັບການຈັດລຽງແຖວຈຳນວນຫຼາຍ, ແຕ່ທ່ານອາດຈະຕ້ອງການກວດສອບໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າຄຳສັ່ງສ"
"ອບຖາມທີ່ຕ້ອງມີການຈັດລຽງຫຼາຍນັ້ນ ໄດ້ໃຊ້ຄໍລຳທີ່ມີດັດສະນີໃນ ORDER BY ເພາະມັນຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ການຈັດລຽງໄວຂຶ້ນຫຼາ"
"ຍ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:242
#, possible-php-format
msgid "Sorted rows average: %s"
msgstr "ຄ່າສະເລ່ຍຂອງແຖວທີ່ຖືກຈັດລຽງ: %s"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:248
msgid "Rate of joins without indexes"
msgstr "ອັດຕາການ Join ໂດຍບໍ່ມີດັດສະນີ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:251
msgid "There are too many joins without indexes."
msgstr "ມີການ Join ໂດຍບໍ່ມີດັດສະນີຫຼາຍເກີນໄປ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:253
msgid ""
"This means that joins are doing full table scans. Adding indexes for the "
"columns being used in the join conditions will greatly speed up table joins."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ໝາຍຄວາມວ່າການ Join ກຳລັງເຮັດການສະແກນຕາຕະລາງທັງໝົດ. ການເພີ່ມດັດສະນີສຳລັບຄໍລຳທີ່ໃຊ້ໃນເງື່ອນໄຂກ"
"ານ Join ຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ການ Join ຕາຕະລາງໄວຂຶ້ນຢ່າງຫຼວງຫຼາຍ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:256
#, possible-php-format
msgid "Table joins average: %s, this value should be less than 1 per hour"
msgstr "ຄ່າສະເລ່ຍການ Join ຕາຕະລາງ: %s, ຄ່ານີ້ຄວນຕ່ຳກວ່າ 1 ຕໍ່ຊົ່ວໂມງ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:261
msgid "Rate of reading first index entry"
msgstr "ອັດຕາການອ່ານຂໍ້ມູນດັດສະນີທຳອິດ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:264
msgid "The rate of reading the first index entry is high."
msgstr "ອັດຕາການອ່ານຂໍ້ມູນດັດສະນີທຳອິດແມ່ນສູງ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:266
msgid ""
"This usually indicates frequent full index scans. Full index scans are "
"faster than table scans but require lots of CPU cycles in big tables, if "
"those tables that have or had high volumes of UPDATEs and DELETEs, running "
"'OPTIMIZE TABLE' might reduce the amount of and/or speed up full index "
"scans. Other than that full index scans can only be reduced by rewriting "
"queries."
msgstr ""
"ໂດຍປົກກະຕິແລ້ວມັນບົ່ງບອກເຖິງການສະແກນດັດສະນີທັງໝົດເລື້ອຍໆ. ການສະແກນດັດສະນີທັງໝົດແມ່ນໄວກວ່າການສະແກ"
"ນຕາຕະລາງທັງໝົດ ແຕ່ຕ້ອງໃຊ້ CPU ຫຼາຍໃນຕາຕະລາງຂະໜາດໃຫຍ່, ຖ້າຕາຕະລາງເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນມີການ UPDATE ແລະ "
"DELETE ເປັນຈຳນວນຫຼາຍ, ການໃຊ້ 'OPTIMIZE TABLE' ອາດຈະຊ່ວຍຫຼຸດ ແລະ/ຫຼື ເພີ່ມຄວາມໄວໃນການສະແ"
"ກນດັດສະນີທັງໝົດໄດ້. ນອກຈາກນັ້ນ, ການສະແກນດັດສະນີທັງໝົດສາມາດຫຼຸດຜ່ອນໄດ້ໂດຍການຂຽນຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມໃໝ່ເທົ່"
"ານັ້ນ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:272
#, possible-php-format
msgid "Index scans average: %s, this value should be less than 1 per hour"
msgstr "ຄ່າສະເລ່ຍການສະແກນດັດສະນີ: %s, ຄ່ານີ້ຄວນຕ່ຳກວ່າ 1 ຕໍ່ຊົ່ວໂມງ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:277
msgid "Rate of reading fixed position"
msgstr "ອັດຕາການອ່ານຈາກຕຳແໜ່ງທີ່ຄົງທີ່"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:280
msgid "The rate of reading data from a fixed position is high."
msgstr "ອັດຕາການອ່ານຂໍ້ມູນຈາກຕຳແໜ່ງທີ່ຄົງທີ່ແມ່ນສູງ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:282
msgid ""
"This indicates that many queries need to sort results and/or do a full table "
"scan, including join queries that do not use indexes. Add indexes where "
"applicable."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ບົ່ງບອກວ່າຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມຈຳນວນຫຼາຍຕ້ອງມີການຈັດລຽງຜົນໄດ້ຮັບ ແລະ/ຫຼື ເຮັດການສະແກນຕາຕະລາງທັງໝົດ, ລວ"
"ມທັງຄຳສັ່ງ Join ທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ໃຊ້ດັດສະນີ. ໃຫ້ເພີ່ມດັດສະນີໃນບ່ອນທີ່ເໝາະສົມ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:285
#, possible-php-format
msgid ""
"Rate of reading fixed position average: %s, this value should be less than 1 "
"per hour"
msgstr "ຄ່າສະເລ່ຍອັດຕາການອ່ານຕຳແໜ່ງທີ່ຄົງທີ່: %s, ຄ່ານີ້ຄວນຕ່ຳກວ່າ 1 ຕໍ່ຊົ່ວໂມງ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:290
msgid "Rate of reading next table row"
msgstr "ອັດຕາການອ່ານແຖວຕໍ່ໄປຂອງຕາຕະລາງ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:293
msgid "The rate of reading the next table row is high."
msgstr "ອັດຕາການອ່ານແຖວຕໍ່ໄປຂອງຕາຕະລາງແມ່ນສູງ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:295
msgid ""
"This indicates that many queries are doing full table scans. Add indexes "
"where applicable."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ບົ່ງບອກວ່າຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມຈຳນວນຫຼາຍກຳລັງເຮັດການສະແກນຕາຕະລາງທັງໝົດ. ໃຫ້ເພີ່ມດັດສະນີໃນບ່ອນທີ່ເໝາະສົມ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:297
#, possible-php-format
msgid ""
"Rate of reading next table row: %s, this value should be less than 1 per hour"
msgstr "ອັດຕາການອ່ານແຖວຕໍ່ໄປຂອງຕາຕະລາງ: %s, ຄ່ານີ້ຄວນຕ່ຳກວ່າ 1 ຕໍ່ຊົ່ວໂມງ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:303
msgid "Different tmp_table_size and max_heap_table_size"
msgstr "ຄ່າ tmp_table_size ແລະ max_heap_table_size ແຕກຕ່າງກັນ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:306
msgid "{tmp_table_size} and {max_heap_table_size} are not the same."
msgstr "{tmp_table_size} ແລະ {max_heap_table_size} ບໍ່ເທົ່າກັນ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:308
msgid ""
"If you have deliberately changed one of either: The server uses the lower "
"value of either to determine the maximum size of in-memory tables. So if you "
"wish to increase the in-memory table limit you will have to increase the "
"other value as well."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າທ່ານເຈດຕະນາປ່ຽນແປງຄ່າໃດໜຶ່ງ: ເຊີເວີຈະໃຊ້ຄ່າທີ່ຕ່ຳກວ່າລະຫວ່າງສອງຄ່ານີ້ເພື່ອມັກຳນົດຂະໜາດສູງສຸດຂອງຕາຕ"
"ະລາງໃນໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳ. ດັ່ງນັ້ນ ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການເພີ່ມຂີດຈຳກັດຂອງຕາຕະລາງໃນໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳ ທ່ານຈະຕ້ອງເພີ່ມອີກ"
"ຄ່າໜຶ່ງນຳ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:312
#, possible-php-format
msgid "Current values are tmp_table_size: %s, max_heap_table_size: %s"
msgstr "ຄ່າປັດຈຸບັນແມ່ນ tmp_table_size: %s, max_heap_table_size: %s"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:318
msgid "Percentage of temp tables on disk"
msgstr "ເປີເຊັນຂອງຕາຕະລາງຊົ່ວຄາວໃນດິສກ໌"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:322
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:343
msgid ""
"Many temporary tables are being written to disk instead of being kept in "
"memory."
msgstr "ມີຕາຕະລາງຊົ່ວຄາວຈຳນວນຫຼາຍຖືກຂຽນລົງດິສກ໌ ແທນທີ່ຈະຖືກເກັບໄວ້ໃນໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:324
msgid ""
"Increasing {max_heap_table_size} and {tmp_table_size} might help. However "
"some temporary tables are always being written to disk, independent of the "
"value of these variables. To eliminate these you will have to rewrite your "
"queries to avoid those conditions (Within a temporary table: Presence of a "
"BLOB or TEXT column or presence of a column bigger than 512 bytes) as "
"mentioned in the beginning of an <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/note.php?"
"note_id=10150111255065841&comments\">Article by the Pythian Group</a>"
msgstr ""
"ການເພີ່ມ {max_heap_table_size} ແລະ {tmp_table_size} ອາດຈະຊ່ວຍໄດ້. ແນວໃດກໍຕາມ ຕາຕະລ"
"າງຊົ່ວຄາວບາງຢ່າງກໍຈະຖືກຂຽນລົງດິສກ໌ສະເໝີ ໂດຍບໍ່ຂຶ້ນກັບຄ່າເຫຼົ່ານີ້. ເພື່ອກຳຈັດບັນຫານີ້ ທ່ານຈະຕ້ອງຂຽນຄຳສັ່ງສອ"
"ບຖາມໃໝ່ເພື່ອຫຼີກລ່ຽງເງື່ອນໄຂເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນ (ພາຍໃນຕາຕະລາງຊົ່ວຄາວ: ມີຄໍລຳ BLOB ຫຼື TEXT ຫຼື ມີຄໍລຳທີ່ມີຂະໜາດໃ"
"ຫຍ່ກວ່າ 512 ໄບຕ໌) ຕາມທີ່ໄດ້ລະບຸໄວ້ໃນ <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/"
"note.php?note_id=10150111255065841&comments\">ບົດຄວາມໂດຍ Pythian Group</a>"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:333
#, possible-php-format
msgid ""
"%s%% of all temporary tables are being written to disk, this value should be "
"below 25%%"
msgstr "%s%% ຂອງຕາຕະລາງຊົ່ວຄາວທັງໝົດຖືກຂຽນລົງດິສກ໌, ຄ່ານີ້ຄວນຕ່ຳກວ່າ 25%%"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:339
msgid "Temp disk rate"
msgstr "ອັດຕາການໃຊ້ດິສກ໌ສຳລັບຂໍ້ມູນຊົ່ວຄາວ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:345
msgid ""
"Increasing {max_heap_table_size} and {tmp_table_size} might help. However "
"some temporary tables are always being written to disk, independent of the "
"value of these variables. To eliminate these you will have to rewrite your "
"queries to avoid those conditions (Within a temporary table: Presence of a "
"BLOB or TEXT column or presence of a column bigger than 512 bytes) as "
"mentioned in the <a href=\"https://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/8.0/en/internal-"
"temporary-tables.html\">MySQL Documentation</a>"
msgstr ""
"ການເພີ່ມຄ່າ {max_heap_table_size} ແລະ {tmp_table_size} ອາດຈະຊ່ວຍໄດ້. ແນວໃດກໍຕາມ ຕາຕ"
"ະລາງຊົ່ວຄາວບາງຢ່າງກໍຖືກຂຽນລົງດິສກ໌ສະເໝີ ໂດຍບໍ່ຂຶ້ນກັບຄ່າເຫຼົ່ານີ້. ເພື່ອແກ້ໄຂບັນຫານີ້ ເຈົ້າຈະຕ້ອງຂຽນຄຳສັ່ງສອ"
"ບຖາມໃໝ່ເພື່ອຫຼີກລ່ຽງເງື່ອນໄຂເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນ ຕາມທີ່ລະບຸໄວ້ໃນ <a href=\"https://dev.mysql.com/doc/"
"refman/8.0/en/internal-temporary-tables.html\">ຄູ່ມື MySQL</a>"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:354
#, possible-php-format
msgid ""
"Rate of temporary tables being written to disk: %s, this value should be "
"less than 1 per hour"
msgstr ""
"ອັດຕາຂອງຕາຕະລາງຊົ່ວຄາວທີ່ຖືກຂຽນລົງດິສກ໌: %s, ຄ່ານີ້ຄວນຕ່ຳກວ່າ 1 ຕໍ່ຊົ່ວໂມງ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:361
msgid "MyISAM key buffer size"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດ MyISAM key buffer"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:364
msgid "Key buffer is not initialized. No MyISAM indexes will be cached."
msgstr "Key buffer ບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ. ຈະບໍ່ມີການແຄຊດັດສະນີ MyISAM."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:366
msgid ""
"Set {key_buffer_size} depending on the size of your MyISAM indexes. 64M is a "
"good start."
msgstr ""
"ຕັ້ງຄ່າ {key_buffer_size} ໂດຍຂຶ້ນກັບຂະໜາດດັດສະນີ MyISAM ຂອງທ່ານ. 64M ແມ່ນການເລີ່ມຕົ້ນທີ່ດີ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:368
msgid "key_buffer_size is 0"
msgstr "key_buffer_size ແມ່ນ 0"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:373
#, no-php-format
msgid "Max % MyISAM key buffer ever used"
msgstr "% ສູງສຸດຂອງ MyISAM key buffer ທີ່ເຄີຍຖືກໃຊ້"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:378
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:395
#, no-php-format
msgid "MyISAM key buffer (index cache) % used is low."
msgstr "ເປີເຊັນການໃຊ້ MyISAM key buffer (index cache) ແມ່ນຕ່ຳ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:380
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:397
msgid ""
"You may need to decrease the size of {key_buffer_size}, re-examine your "
"tables to see if indexes have been removed, or examine queries and "
"expectations about what indexes are being used."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານອາດຈະຕ້ອງຫຼຸດຂະໜາດຂອງ {key_buffer_size}, ກວດສອບຕາຕະລາງຂອງທ່ານຄືນໃໝ່ວ່າມີດັດສະນີໃດຖືກລຶ"
"ບອອກບໍ່, ຫຼື ກວດສອບຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມ ແລະ ສິ່ງທີ່ຄາດຫວັງກ່ຽວກັບດັດສະນີທີ່ກຳລັງຖືກໃຊ້."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:384
#, possible-php-format
msgid ""
"max %% MyISAM key buffer ever used: %s%%, this value should be above 95%%"
msgstr ""
"ເປີເຊັນສູງສຸດຂອງ MyISAM key buffer ທີ່ເຄີຍໃຊ້: %s%%, ຄ່ານີ້ຄວນສູງກວ່າ 95%%"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:389
msgid "Percentage of MyISAM key buffer used"
msgstr "ເປີເຊັນຂອງ MyISAM key buffer ທີ່ຖືກໃຊ້"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:401
#, possible-php-format
msgid "%% MyISAM key buffer used: %s%%, this value should be above 95%%"
msgstr "%% ຂອງ MyISAM key buffer ທີ່ຖືກໃຊ້: %s%%, ຄ່ານີ້ຄວນສູງກວ່າ 95%%"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:406
msgid "Percentage of index reads from memory"
msgstr "ເປີເຊັນຂອງການອ່ານດັດສະນີຈາກໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:411
#, no-php-format
msgid "The % of indexes that use the MyISAM key buffer is low."
msgstr "ເປີເຊັນຂອງອິນເດັກທີ່ໃຊ້ MyISAM key buffer ແມ່ນຕ່ຳ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:412
msgid "You may need to increase {key_buffer_size}."
msgstr "ທ່ານອາດຈະຕ້ອງເພີ່ມຄ່າ {key_buffer_size}."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:413
#, possible-php-format
msgid "Index reads from memory: %s%%, this value should be above 95%%"
msgstr "ການອ່ານດັດສະນີຈາກໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳ: %s%%, ຄ່ານີ້ຄວນສູງກວ່າ 95%%"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:419
msgid "Rate of table open"
msgstr "ອັດຕາການເປີດຕາຕະລາງ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:422
msgid "The rate of opening tables is high."
msgstr "ອັດຕາການເປີດຕາຕະລາງແມ່ນສູງ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:424
msgid ""
"Opening tables requires disk I/O which is costly. Increasing "
"{table_open_cache} might avoid this."
msgstr ""
"ການເປີດຕາຕະລາງຕ້ອງໃຊ້ Disk I/O ເຊິ່ງມີຕົ້ນທຶນສູງ. ການເພີ່ມ {table_open_cache} ອາດຈະຊ່ວຍຫຼີກລ່"
"ຽງບັນຫານີ້ໄດ້."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:427
#, possible-php-format
msgid "Opened table rate: %s, this value should be less than 10 per hour"
msgstr "ອັດຕາການເປີດຕາຕະລາງ: %s, ຄ່ານີ້ຄວນຕ່ຳກວ່າ 10 ຕໍ່ຊົ່ວໂມງ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:432
msgid "Percentage of used open files limit"
msgstr "ເປີເຊັນຂອງການໃຊ້ຂີດຈຳກັດການເປີດໄຟລ໌"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:436
msgid ""
"The number of open files is approaching the max number of open files. You "
"may get a \"Too many open files\" error."
msgstr ""
"ຈຳນວນໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເປີດຢູ່ກຳລັງໃກ້ຈະຮອດຂີດຈຳກັດສູງສຸດ. ເຈົ້າອາດຈະພົບຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ \"Too many open files\"."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:440
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:453
msgid ""
"Consider increasing {open_files_limit}, and check the error log when "
"restarting after changing {open_files_limit}."
msgstr ""
"ພິຈາລະນາເພີ່ມ {open_files_limit}, ແລະ ກວດສອບ error log ເມື່ອເຮັດການຣີສະຕາດຫຼັງຈາກປ່ຽນຄ່"
"າ {open_files_limit}."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:443
#, possible-php-format
msgid ""
"The number of opened files is at %s%% of the limit. It should be below 85%%"
msgstr "ຈຳນວນໄຟລ໌ທີ່ຖືກເປີດຢູ່ທີ່ %s%% ຂອງຂີດຈຳກັດ. ມັນຄວນຈະຕ່ຳກວ່າ 85%%"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:448
msgid "Rate of open files"
msgstr "ອັດຕາການເປີດໄຟລ໌"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:451
msgid "The rate of opening files is high."
msgstr "ອັດຕາການເປີດໄຟລ໌ແມ່ນສູງ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:456
#, possible-php-format
msgid "Opened files rate: %s, this value should be less than 5 per hour"
msgstr "ອັດຕາການເປີດໄຟລ໌: %s, ຄ່ານີ້ຄວນຕ່ຳກວ່າ 5 ຕໍ່ຊົ່ວໂມງ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:462
#, no-php-format
msgid "Immediate table locks %"
msgstr "ເປີເຊັນການລັອກຕາຕະລາງທັນທີ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:466
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:476
msgid "Too many table locks were not granted immediately."
msgstr "ມີການລັອກຕາຕະລາງຫຼາຍເກີນໄປທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ຮັບການອະນຸຍາດທັນທີ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:467
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:477
msgid "Optimize queries and/or use InnoDB to reduce lock wait."
msgstr "ປັບແຕ່ງຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມ ແລະ/ຫຼື ໃຊ້ InnoDB ເພື່ອຫຼຸດເວລາລໍຖ້າການລັອກ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:468
#, possible-php-format
msgid "Immediate table locks: %s%%, this value should be above 95%%"
msgstr "ການລັອກຕາຕະລາງທັນທີ: %s%%, ຄ່ານີ້ຄວນສູງກວ່າ 95%%"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:473
msgid "Table lock wait rate"
msgstr "ອັດຕາການລໍຖ້າການລັອກຕາຕະລາງ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:478
#, possible-php-format
msgid "Table lock wait rate: %s, this value should be less than 1 per hour"
msgstr "ອັດຕາການລໍຖ້າການລັອກຕາຕະລາງ: %s, ຄ່ານີ້ຄວນຕ່ຳກວ່າ 1 ຕໍ່ຊົ່ວໂມງ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:483
msgid "Thread cache"
msgstr "Thread cache"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:486
msgid ""
"Thread cache is disabled, resulting in more overhead from new connections to "
"MySQL."
msgstr ""
"Thread cache ຖືກປິດໃຊ້ງານ, ເຮັດໃຫ້ເກີດ overhead ຫຼາຍຂຶ້ນຈາກການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ໃໝ່ຫາ MySQL."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:487
msgid "Enable the thread cache by setting {thread_cache_size} > 0."
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ Thread cache ໂດຍການຕັ້ງຄ່າ {thread_cache_size} > 0."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:488
msgid "The thread cache is set to 0"
msgstr "Thread cache ຖືກຕັ້ງເປັນ 0"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:493
#, no-php-format
msgid "Thread cache hit rate %"
msgstr "ອັດຕາການພົບຂໍ້ມູນໃນແຄຊ໌ຂອງເທຣດ %"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:497
msgid "Thread cache is not efficient."
msgstr "Thread cache ບໍ່ມີປະສິດທິພາບ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:498
msgid "Increase {thread_cache_size}."
msgstr "ເພີ່ມ {thread_cache_size}."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:499
#, possible-php-format
msgid "Thread cache hitrate: %s%%, this value should be above 80%%"
msgstr "Thread cache hitrate: %s%%, ຄ່ານີ້ຄວນສູງກວ່າ 80%%"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:504
msgid "Threads that are slow to launch"
msgstr "ເທຣດທີ່ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຊ້າ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:508
msgid "There are too many threads that are slow to launch."
msgstr "ມີເທຣດຈຳນວນຫຼາຍເກີນໄປທີ່ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຊ້າ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:510
msgid ""
"This generally happens in case of general system overload as it is pretty "
"simple operations. You might want to monitor your system load carefully."
msgstr ""
"ໂດຍທົ່ວໄປແລ້ວມັນຈະເກີດຂຶ້ນໃນກໍລະນີທີ່ລະບົບເຮັດວຽກໜັກເກີນໄປ ເພາະມັນເປັນການເຮັດວຽກທີ່ຂ້ອນຂ້າງງ່າຍດາຍ. "
"ທ່ານອາດຈະຕ້ອງການຕິດຕາມການເຮັດວຽກຂອງລະບົບຢ່າງລະມັດລະວັງ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:513
#, possible-php-format
msgid "%s thread(s) took longer than %s seconds to start, it should be 0"
msgstr "ມີ %s ເທຣດທີ່ໃຊ້ເວລາດົນກວ່າ %s ວິນາທີໃນການເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ, ມັນຄວນຈະເປັນ 0"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:518
msgid "Slow launch time"
msgstr "ເວລາການເລີ່ມຕົ້ນທີ່ຊ້າ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:521
msgid "Slow_launch_time is above 2s."
msgstr "Slow_launch_time ສູງກວ່າ 2 ວິນາທີ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:523
msgid ""
"Set {slow_launch_time} to 1s or 2s to correctly count threads that are slow "
"to launch."
msgstr ""
"ຕັ້ງຄ່າ {slow_launch_time} ເປັນ 1 ວິນາທີ ຫຼື 2 ວິນາທີ ເພື່ອນັບຈຳນວນເທຣດທີ່ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຊ້າໃຫ້ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:525
#, possible-php-format
msgid "slow_launch_time is set to %s"
msgstr "slow_launch_time ຖືກຕັ້ງເປັນ %s"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:531
msgid "Percentage of used connections"
msgstr "ເປີເຊັນຂອງການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ທີ່ຖືກໃຊ້"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:535
msgid ""
"The maximum amount of used connections is getting close to the value of "
"{max_connections}."
msgstr "ຈຳນວນການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ສູງສຸດທີ່ຖືກໃຊ້ກຳລັງເຂົ້າໃກ້ຄ່າຂອງ {max_connections}."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:538
msgid ""
"Increase {max_connections}, or decrease {wait_timeout} so that connections "
"that do not close database handlers properly get killed sooner. Make sure "
"the code closes database handlers properly."
msgstr ""
"ເພີ່ມ {max_connections}, ຫຼື ຫຼຸດ {wait_timeout} ເພື່ອໃຫ້ການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ປິດ database "
"handlers ຢ່າງຖືກຕ້ອງຖືກຍົກເລີກໄວຂຶ້ນ. ກວດສອບໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າໂຄ້ດໄດ້ປິດ database handlers ຢ່າງເໝາະ"
"ສົມ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:542
#, possible-php-format
msgid ""
"Max_used_connections is at %s%% of max_connections, it should be below 80%%"
msgstr ""
"Max_used_connections ຢູ່ທີ່ %s%% ຂອງ max_connections, ມັນຄວນຈະຕ່ຳກວ່າ 80%%"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:547
msgid "Percentage of aborted connections"
msgstr "ເປີເຊັນຂອງການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ທີ່ຖືກຍົກເລີກ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:550
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:564
msgid "Too many connections are aborted."
msgstr "ມີການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ຈຳນວນຫຼາຍເກີນໄປທີ່ຖືກຍົກເລີກ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:552
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:566
msgid ""
"Connections are usually aborted when they cannot be authorized. <a "
"href=\"https://www.percona.com/blog/2008/08/23/how-to-track-down-the-source-"
"of-aborted_connects/\">This article</a> might help you track down the source."
msgstr ""
"ການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ມັກຈະຖືກຍົກເລີກເມື່ອບໍ່ສາມາດກວດສອບສິດໄດ້. <a href=\"https://www.percona.com/"
"blog/2008/08/23/how-to-track-down-the-source-of-aborted_connects/\"><a "
"href=\"https://www.percona.com/blog/2008/08/23/how-to-track-down-the-source-"
"of-aborted_connects/\">ບົດຄວາມນີ້</a> ອາດຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານຕິດຕາມຫາສາເຫດໄດ້."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:556
#, possible-php-format
msgid "%s%% of all connections are aborted. This value should be below 1%%"
msgstr "%s%% ຂອງການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ທັງໝົດຖືກຍົກເລີກ. ຄ່ານີ້ຄວນຕ່ຳກວ່າ 1%%"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:561
msgid "Rate of aborted connections"
msgstr "ອັດຕາການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ທີ່ຖືກຍົກເລີກ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:570
#, possible-php-format
msgid ""
"Aborted connections rate is at %s, this value should be less than 1 per hour"
msgstr "ອັດຕາການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ທີ່ຖືກຍົກເລີກຢູ່ທີ່ %s, ຄ່ານີ້ຄວນຕ່ຳກວ່າ 1 ຕໍ່ຊົ່ວໂມງ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:575
msgid "Percentage of aborted clients"
msgstr "ເປີເຊັນຂອງໄຄລເອັນທ໌ (clients) ທີ່ຖືກຍົກເລີກ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:578
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:592
msgid "Too many clients are aborted."
msgstr "ມີໄຄລເອັນທ໌ຈຳນວນຫຼາຍເກີນໄປທີ່ຖືກຍົກເລີກ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:580
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:594
msgid ""
"Clients are usually aborted when they did not close their connection to "
"MySQL properly. This can be due to network issues or code not closing a "
"database handler properly. Check your network and code."
msgstr ""
"ໄຄລເອັນທ໌ມັກຈະຖືກຍົກເລີກເມື່ອພວກເຂົາບໍ່ໄດ້ປິດການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັບ MySQL ຢ່າງຖືກຕ້ອງ. ສິ່ງນີ້ອາດຈະເກີດຈາກບັນຫາ"
"ເຄືອຂ່າຍ ຫຼື ໂຄ້ດທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ປິດ database handler ຢ່າງຖືກຕ້ອງ. ໃຫ້ກວດສອບເຄືອຂ່າຍ ແລະ ໂຄ້ດຂອງທ່ານ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:584
#, possible-php-format
msgid "%s%% of all clients are aborted. This value should be below 2%%"
msgstr "%s%% ຂອງໄຄລເອັນທ໌ທັງໝົດຖືກຍົກເລີກ. ຄ່ານີ້ຄວນຕ່ຳກວ່າ 2%%"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:589
msgid "Rate of aborted clients"
msgstr "ອັດຕາຂອງໄຄລເອັນທ໌ທີ່ຖືກຍົກເລີກ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:598
#, possible-php-format
msgid "Aborted client rate is at %s, this value should be less than 1 per hour"
msgstr "ອັດຕາໄຄລເອັນທ໌ທີ່ຖືກຍົກເລີກຢູ່ທີ່ %s, ຄ່ານີ້ຄວນຕ່ຳກວ່າ 1 ຕໍ່ຊົ່ວໂມງ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:604
msgid "Is InnoDB disabled?"
msgstr "InnoDB ຖືກປິດໃຊ້ງານຢູ່ບໍ່?"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:608
msgid "You do not have InnoDB enabled."
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ໄດ້ເປີດໃຊ້ງານ InnoDB."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:609
msgid "InnoDB is usually the better choice for table engines."
msgstr "ໂດຍປົກກະຕິແລ້ວ InnoDB ແມ່ນທາງເລືອກທີ່ດີກວ່າສຳລັບ table engines."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:610
msgid "have_innodb is set to 'value'"
msgstr "have_innodb ຖືກຕັ້ງເປັນ 'value'"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:614
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:640
msgid "InnoDB log size"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດ InnoDB log"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:619
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:648
msgid ""
"The InnoDB log file size is not an appropriate size, in relation to the "
"InnoDB buffer pool."
msgstr "ຂະໜາດຂອງ InnoDB log file ບໍ່ເໝາະສົມ ເມື່ອທຽບກັບ InnoDB buffer pool."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:622
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:651
#, no-php-format
msgid ""
"Especially on a system with a lot of writes to InnoDB tables you should set "
"{innodb_log_file_size} to 25% of {innodb_buffer_pool_size}. However the "
"bigger this value, the longer the recovery time will be when database "
"crashes, so this value should not be set much higher than 256 MiB. Please "
"note however that you cannot simply change the value of this variable. You "
"need to shutdown the server, remove the InnoDB log files, set the new value "
"in my.cnf, start the server, then check the error logs if everything went "
"fine. See also <a href=\"https://mysqldatabaseadministration.blogspot."
"com/2007/01/increase-innodblogfilesize-proper-way.html\">this blog entry</a>"
msgstr ""
"ໂດຍສະເພາະໃນລະບົບທີ່ມີການຂຽນລົງຕາຕະລາງ InnoDB ຫຼາຍ ເຈົ້າຄວນຕັ້ງ {innodb_log_file_size} ເ"
"ປັນ 25% ຂອງ {innodb_buffer_pool_size}. ແນວໃດກໍຕາມ ຍິ່ງຄ່ານີ້ຫຼາຍເທົ່າໃດ ເວລາໃນການກູ້ຄືນ "
"(recovery) ກໍຈະຍິ່ງດົນຂຶ້ນເມື່ອຖານຂໍ້ມູນພັງ, ດັ່ງນັ້ນ ຄ່ານີ້ບໍ່ຄວນຕັ້ງໃຫ້ສູງກວ່າ 256 MiB ຫຼາຍເກີນໄປ. ໝາຍເ"
"ຫດ: ເຈົ້າບໍ່ສາມາດປ່ຽນຄ່າຕົວປ່ຽນນີ້ໄດ້ທັນທີ. ເຈົ້າຕ້ອງປິດເຊີເວີ, ລຶບໄຟລ໌ລັອກຂອງ InnoDB ອອກ, ຕັ້ງຄ່າໃໝ່ໃ"
"ນ my.cnf, ເລີ່ມເຊີເວີໃໝ່, ແລ້ວກວດສອບ error logs ວ່າທຸກຢ່າງຮຽບຮ້ອຍດີບໍ່. ເບິ່ງເພີ່ມເຕີມໄດ້ທີ່ <a "
"href=\"https://mysqldatabaseadministration.blogspot.com/2007/01/increase-"
"innodblogfilesize-proper-way.html\">ບົດຄວາມນີ້</a>"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:633
#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:662
#, possible-php-format
msgid ""
"Your InnoDB log size is at %s%% in relation to the InnoDB buffer pool size, "
"it should not be below 20%%"
msgstr ""
"ຂະໜາດ InnoDB log ຂອງທ່ານຢູ່ທີ່ %s%% ເມື່ອທຽບກັບຂະໜາດ InnoDB buffer pool, ມັນບໍ່ຄວນຕ່ຳກວ່າ "
"20%%"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:669
msgid "Max InnoDB log size"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດ InnoDB log ສູງສຸດ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:673
msgid "The InnoDB log file size is inadequately large."
msgstr "ຂະໜາດໄຟລ໌ InnoDB log ໃຫຍ່ເກີນຄວາມຈຳເປັນ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:675
#, no-php-format
msgid ""
"It is usually sufficient to set {innodb_log_file_size} to 25% of the size of "
"{innodb_buffer_pool_size}. A very big {innodb_log_file_size} slows down the "
"recovery time after a database crash considerably. See also <a "
"href=\"https://www.percona.com/blog/2006/07/03/choosing-proper-"
"innodb_log_file_size/\">this Article</a>. You need to shutdown the server, "
"remove the InnoDB log files, set the new value in my.cnf, start the server, "
"then check the error logs if everything went fine. See also <a "
"href=\"https://mysqldatabaseadministration.blogspot.com/2007/01/increase-"
"innodblogfilesize-proper-way.html\">this blog entry</a>"
msgstr ""
"ໂດຍທົ່ວໄປແລ້ວພຽງແຕ່ຕັ້ງ {innodb_log_file_size} ເປັນ 25% ຂອງ "
"{innodb_buffer_pool_size} ກໍພຽງພໍແລ້ວ. ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ {innodb_log_file_size} ທີ່ໃຫຍ່ຫຼາຍຈະເ"
"ຮັດໃຫ້ການກູ້ຄືນຫຼັງຈາກຖານຂໍ້ມູນພັງນັ້ນຊ້າລົງຫຼາຍ. ເບິ່ງເພີ່ມເຕີມໄດ້ທີ່ <a href=\"https://"
"www.percona.com/blog/2006/07/03/choosing-proper-innodb_log_file_size/\">ບົດຄວາ"
"ມນີ້</a>. ເຈົ້າຕ້ອງປິດເຊີເວີ, ລຶບໄຟລ໌ລັອກຂອງ InnoDB ອອກ, ຕັ້ງຄ່າໃໝ່ໃນ my.cnf, ເລີ່ມເຊີເວີໃໝ່, ແລ້ວ"
"ກວດສອບ error logs ວ່າທຸກຢ່າງຮຽບຮ້ອຍດີບໍ່. ເບິ່ງເພີ່ມເຕີມໄດ້ທີ່ <a href=\"https://"
"mysqldatabaseadministration.blogspot.com/2007/01/increase-innodblogfilesize-"
"proper-way.html\">ບົດຄວາມນີ້</a>"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:685
#, possible-php-format
msgid "Your absolute InnoDB log size is %s MiB"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດ InnoDB log ທີ່ແນ່ນອນຂອງທ່ານແມ່ນ %s MiB"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:690
msgid "InnoDB buffer pool size"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດ InnoDB buffer pool"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:694
msgid "Your InnoDB buffer pool is fairly small."
msgstr "InnoDB buffer pool ຂອງທ່ານຂ້ອນຂ້າງນ້ອຍ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:696
#, no-php-format
msgid ""
"The InnoDB buffer pool has a profound impact on performance for InnoDB "
"tables. Assign all your remaining memory to this buffer. For database "
"servers that use solely InnoDB as storage engine and have no other services "
"(e.g. a web server) running, you may set this as high as 80% of your "
"available memory. If that is not the case, you need to carefully assess the "
"memory consumption of your other services and non-InnoDB-Tables and set this "
"variable accordingly. If it is set too high, your system will start "
"swapping, which decreases performance significantly. See also <a "
"href=\"https://www.percona.com/blog/2007/11/03/choosing-"
"innodb_buffer_pool_size/\">this article</a>"
msgstr ""
"InnoDB buffer pool ມີຜົນກະທົບຢ່າງຫຼາຍຕໍ່ປະສິດທິພາບຂອງຕາຕະລາງ InnoDB. ໃຫ້ກຳນົດຄວາມຈຳທີ່ເຫຼືອທັ"
"ງໝົດໃຫ້ກັບບັບເຟີນີ້. ສຳລັບເຊີເວີຖານຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ໃຊ້ສະເພາະ InnoDB ເປັນ Storage Engine ແລະ ບໍ່ມີບໍລິການອື່ນ"
"ໆ (ເຊັ່ນ Web Server) ລັນຢູ່, ເຈົ້າອາດຈະຕັ້ງຄ່ານີ້ໄດ້ສູງເຖິງ 80% ຂອງຄວາມຈຳທີ່ມີຢູ່. ຖ້າບໍ່ແມ່ນແນວນັ້ນ, ເ"
"ຈົ້າຕ້ອງປະເມີນການໃຊ້ຄວາມຈຳຂອງບໍລິການອື່ນໆ ແລະ ຕາຕະລາງທີ່ບໍ່ແມ່ນ InnoDB ຢ່າງລະມັດລະວັງ ແລະ ຕັ້ງຄ່າ"
"ຕົວປ່ຽນນີ້ໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມ. ຖ້າຕັ້ງໄວ້ສູງເກີນໄປ, ລະບົບຈະເລີ່ມໃຊ້ Swapping ເຊິ່ງຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ປະສິດທິພາບຫຼຸດລົງຢ່າງ"
"ຫຼວງຫຼາຍ. ເບິ່ງເພີ່ມເຕີມໄດ້ທີ່ <a href=\"https://www.percona.com/blog/2007/11/03/"
"choosing-innodb_buffer_pool_size/\">ບົດຄວາມນີ້</a>"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:706
#, possible-php-format
msgid ""
"You are currently using %s%% of your memory for the InnoDB buffer pool. This "
"rule fires if you are assigning less than 60%%, however this might be "
"perfectly adequate for your system if you don't have much InnoDB tables or "
"other services running on the same machine."
msgstr ""
"ໃນປັດຈຸບັນທ່ານກຳລັງໃຊ້ %s%% ຂອງຄວາມຈຳຂອງທ່ານສຳລັບ InnoDB buffer pool. ກົດເກນນີ້ຈະເຮັດວຽກຖ້"
"າທ່ານກຳນົດໄວ້ຕ່ຳກວ່າ 60%%, ແນວໃດກໍຕາມ ມັນອາດຈະພຽງພໍແລ້ວສຳລັບລະບົບຂອງທ່ານ ຖ້າທ່ານບໍ່ມີຕາຕະລາງ "
"InnoDB ຫຼາຍ ຫຼື ບໍ່ມີບໍລິການອື່ນໆທີ່ເຮັດວຽກຢູ່ໃນເຄື່ອງດຽວກັນ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:716
msgid "MyISAM concurrent inserts"
msgstr "MyISAM concurrent inserts"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:719
msgid "Enable {concurrent_insert} by setting it to 1"
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ {concurrent_insert} ໂດຍການຕັ້ງຄ່າເປັນ 1"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:721
msgid ""
"Setting {concurrent_insert} to 1 reduces contention between readers and "
"writers for a given table. See also <a href=\"https://dev.mysql.com/doc/"
"refman/5.5/en/concurrent-inserts.html\">MySQL Documentation</a>"
msgstr ""
"ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ {concurrent_insert} ເປັນ 1 ຈະຊ່ວຍຫຼຸດຜ່ອນການຍາດແຍ່ງລະຫວ່າງຜູ້ອ່ານ ແລະ ຜູ້ຂຽນຂໍ້ມູນໃນ"
"ຕາຕະລາງ. ເບິ່ງເພີ່ມເຕີມໄດ້ທີ່ <a href=\"https://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/5.5/en/"
"concurrent-inserts.html\">ເອກະສານ MySQL</a>"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_generic.php:725
msgid "concurrent_insert is set to 0"
msgstr "concurrent_insert ຖືກຕັ້ງເປັນ 0"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:9
msgid "Query cache disabled"
msgstr "Query cache ຖືກປິດໃຊ້ງານ"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:12
msgid "The query cache is not enabled."
msgstr "Query cache ບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກເປີດໃຊ້ງານ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:14
msgid ""
"The query cache is known to greatly improve performance if configured "
"correctly. Enable it by setting {query_cache_size} to a 2 digit MiB value "
"and setting {query_cache_type} to 'ON'. <b>Note:</b> If you are using "
"memcached, ignore this recommendation."
msgstr ""
"Query cache ເປັນທີ່ຮູ້ຈັກກັນດີວ່າມັນຊ່ວຍປັບປຸງປະສິດທິພາບໄດ້ຢ່າງຫຼວງຫຼາຍຖ້າຕັ້ງຄ່າຢ່າງຖືກຕ້ອງ. ເປີດໃຊ້ມັນໂດ"
"ຍການຕັ້ງຄ່າ {query_cache_size} ເປັນຄ່າ MiB ທີ່ມີ 2 ຫຼັກ ແລະ ຕັ້ງ {query_cache_type} ເປັນ "
"'ON'. <b>ໝາຍເຫດ:</b> ຖ້າທ່ານກຳລັງໃຊ້ memcached ໃຫ້ຂ້າມຄຳແນະນຳນີ້."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:18
msgid "query_cache_size is set to 0 or query_cache_type is set to 'OFF'"
msgstr "query_cache_size ຖືກຕັ້ງເປັນ 0 ຫຼື query_cache_type ຖືກຕັ້ງເປັນ 'OFF'"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:23
#, no-php-format
msgid "Query cache efficiency (%)"
msgstr "ປະສິດທິພາບຂອງ Query cache (%)"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:27
msgid "Query cache not running efficiently, it has a low hit rate."
msgstr "Query cache ເຮັດວຽກບໍ່ມີປະສິດທິພາບ, ມັນມີອັດຕາການ hit ຕ່ຳ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:28
msgid "Consider increasing {query_cache_limit}."
msgstr "ພິຈາລະນາເພີ່ມ {query_cache_limit}."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:29
#, possible-php-format
msgid "The current query cache hit rate of %s%% is below 20%%"
msgstr "ອັດຕາການ hit ຂອງ query cache ໃນປັດຈຸບັນແມ່ນ %s%% ເຊິ່ງຕ່ຳກວ່າ 20%%"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:34
msgid "Query Cache usage"
msgstr "ການໃຊ້ Query Cache"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:39
#, no-php-format
msgid "Less than 80% of the query cache is being utilized."
msgstr "ມີການໃຊ້ງານ Query cache ໜ້ອຍກວ່າ 80%."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:41
msgid ""
"This might be caused by {query_cache_limit} being too low. Flushing the "
"query cache might help as well."
msgstr ""
"ສິ່ງນີ້ອາດຈະເກີດຈາກ {query_cache_limit} ຕ່ຳເກີນໄປ. ການລ້າງ (flushing) query cache ກໍອາ"
"ດຈະຊ່ວຍໄດ້ຄືກັນ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:45
#, possible-php-format
msgid ""
"The current ratio of free query cache memory to total query cache size is "
"%s%%. It should be above 80%%"
msgstr ""
"ອັດຕາສ່ວນຂອງຄວາມຈຳ query cache ທີ່ຫວ່າງທຽບກັບຂະໜາດທັງໝົດແມ່ນ %s%%. ມັນຄວນຈະສູງກວ່າ 80%%"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:52
msgid "Query cache fragmentation"
msgstr "ການແຕກແຍກ (fragmentation) ຂອງ Query cache"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:56
msgid "The query cache is considerably fragmented."
msgstr "Query cache ມີການແຕກແຍກຂ້ອນຂ້າງຫຼາຍ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:58
msgid ""
"Severe fragmentation is likely to (further) increase Qcache_lowmem_prunes. "
"This might be caused by many Query cache low memory prunes due to "
"{query_cache_size} being too small. For a immediate but short lived fix you "
"can flush the query cache (might lock the query cache for a long time). "
"Carefully adjusting {query_cache_min_res_unit} to a lower value might help "
"too, e.g. you can set it to the average size of your queries in the cache "
"using this formula: (query_cache_size - qcache_free_memory) / "
"qcache_queries_in_cache"
msgstr ""
"ການແຕກແຍກທີ່ຮຸນແຮງອາດຈະເພີ່ມ Qcache_lowmem_prunes ຫຼາຍຂຶ້ນ. ສິ່ງນີ້ອາດຈະເກີດຈາກການ prunes "
"ຍ້ອນຄວາມຈຳຕ່ຳ ເພາະ {query_cache_size} ນ້ອຍເກີນໄປ. ສຳລັບການແກ້ໄຂຊົ່ວຄາວທ່ານສາມາດ flush "
"query cache ໄດ້ (ແຕ່ອາດຈະລັອກ query cache ໄວ້ດົນ). ການປັບ "
"{query_cache_min_res_unit} ໃຫ້ຕ່ຳລົງກໍອາດຈະຊ່ວຍໄດ້."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:66
#, possible-php-format
msgid ""
"The cache is currently fragmented by %s%% , with 100%% fragmentation meaning "
"that the query cache is an alternating pattern of free and used blocks. This "
"value should be below 20%%."
msgstr ""
"ໃນປັດຈຸບັນ cache ມີການແຕກແຍກຢູ່ທີ່ %s%%, ໂດຍການແຕກແຍກ 100%% ໝາຍຄວາມວ່າ query cache ມີລັກ"
"ສະນະສະຫຼັບກັນລະຫວ່າງບລັອກທີ່ຫວ່າງ ແລະ ບລັອກທີ່ຖືກໃຊ້. ຄ່ານີ້ຄວນຕ່ຳກວ່າ 20%%."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:73
msgid "Query cache low memory prunes"
msgstr "Query cache low memory prunes"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:77
msgid ""
"Cached queries are removed due to low query cache memory from the query "
"cache."
msgstr ""
"ຄຳສັ່ງສອບຖາມທີ່ຖືກແຄຊໄວ້ຖືກລຶບອອກຈາກ query cache ຍ້ອນວ່າຄວາມຈຳ query cache ຕ່ຳ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:79
msgid ""
"You might want to increase {query_cache_size}, however keep in mind that the "
"overhead of maintaining the cache is likely to increase with its size, so do "
"this in small increments and monitor the results."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານອາດຈະຕ້ອງການເພີ່ມ {query_cache_size}, ແນວໃດກໍຕາມ ໃຫ້ຈື່ໄວ້ວ່າ overhead ໃນການຮັກສາ "
"cache ຈະເພີ່ມຂຶ້ນຕາມຂະໜາດຂອງມັນ, ດັ່ງນັ້ນໃຫ້ຄ່ອຍໆເພີ່ມເທື່ອລະໜ້ອຍ ແລະ ຕິດຕາມຜົນ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:84
#, possible-php-format
msgid ""
"The ratio of removed queries to inserted queries is %s%%. The lower this "
"value is, the better (This rules firing limit: 0.1%%)"
msgstr ""
"ອັດຕາສ່ວນຂອງຄຳສັ່ງທີ່ຖືກລຶບອອກທຽບກັບຄຳສັ່ງທີ່ຖືກເພີ່ມເຂົ້າແມ່ນ %s%%. ຍິ່ງຄ່ານີ້ຕ່ຳເທົ່າໃດກໍຍິ່ງດີ (ຂີດຈຳກັດຂອງ"
"ກົດເກນນີ້ແມ່ນ: 0.1%%)"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:91
msgid "Query cache max size"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດສູງສຸດຂອງ Query cache"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:96
msgid ""
"The query cache size is above 128 MiB. Big query caches may cause "
"significant overhead that is required to maintain the cache."
msgstr ""
"ຂະໜາດຂອງ query cache ສູງກວ່າ 128 MiB. query cache ທີ່ໃຫຍ່ເກີນໄປອາດຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ເກີດ "
"overhead ຫຼາຍໃນການຮັກສາ cache."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:100
msgid ""
"Depending on your environment, it might be performance increasing to reduce "
"this value."
msgstr ""
"ຂຶ້ນກັບສະພາບແວດລ້ອມການໃຊ້ງານຂອງທ່ານ, ການຫຼຸດຄ່ານີ້ລົງອາດຈະຊ່ວຍເພີ່ມປະສິດທິພາບໄດ້."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:102
#, possible-php-format
msgid "Current query cache size: %s"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດ query cache ປັດຈຸບັນ: %s"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:107
msgid "Query cache min result size"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດຜົນໄດ້ຮັບຕ່ຳສຸດຂອງ Query cache"

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:111
msgid ""
"The max size of the result set in the query cache is the default of 1 MiB."
msgstr "ຂະໜາດສູງສຸດຂອງຜົນໄດ້ຮັບໃນ query cache ແມ່ນຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນທີ່ 1 MiB."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:113
msgid ""
"Changing {query_cache_limit} (usually by increasing) may increase "
"efficiency. This variable determines the maximum size a query result may "
"have to be inserted into the query cache. If there are many query results "
"above 1 MiB that are well cacheable (many reads, little writes) then "
"increasing {query_cache_limit} will increase efficiency. Whereas in the case "
"of many query results being above 1 MiB that are not very well cacheable "
"(often invalidated due to table updates) increasing {query_cache_limit} "
"might reduce efficiency."
msgstr ""
"ການປ່ຽນແປງ {query_cache_limit} (ໂດຍປົກກະຕິແມ່ນການເພີ່ມຂຶ້ນ) ອາດຈະຊ່ວຍເພີ່ມປະສິດທິພາບໄດ້. ຕົວ"
"ປ່ຽນນີ້ກຳນົດຂະໜາດສູງສຸດຂອງຜົນໄດ້ຮັບທີ່ຈະຖືກເກັບໃນ query cache. ຖ້າມີຜົນໄດ້ຮັບຫຼາຍກວ່າ 1 MiB ທີ່ສາມາ"
"ດເຮັດ cache ໄດ້ດີ ການເພີ່ມຄ່ານີ້ຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ດີຂຶ້ນ. ແຕ່ຖ້າຜົນໄດ້ຮັບນັ້ນມີການປ່ຽນແປງເລື້ອຍໆ ການເພີ່ມຄ່ານີ້ກໍອາດ"
"ຈະຫຼຸດປະສິດທິພາບລົງ."

#: libraries/advisory_rules_mysql_before80003.php:120
msgid "query_cache_limit is set to 1 MiB"
msgstr "query_cache_limit ຖືກຕັ້ງເປັນ 1 MiB"

