"ທ່ານມີການປ່ຽນແປງທີ່ຍັງບໍ່ທັນໄດ້ບັນທຶກ; ທ່ານແນ່ໃຈຫຼືບໍ່ວ່າຈະອອກຈາກໜ້ານີ້?"

#: libraries/classes/Controllers/JavaScriptMessagesController.php:56
msgid ""
"You are trying to reduce the number of rows, but have already entered data "
"in those rows which will be lost. Do you wish to continue?"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານກຳລັງພະຍາຍາມຫຼຸດຈຳນວນແຖວ, ແຕ່ມີຂໍ້ມູນຢູ່ໃນແຖວເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນແລ້ວເຊິ່ງຈະສູນຫາຍໄປ. ຕ້ອງການເຮັດຕໍ່ຫຼືບໍ່?"

#: libraries/classes/Controllers/JavaScriptMessagesController.php:59
msgid "Do you really want to revoke the selected user(s) ?"
msgstr "ທ່ານຕ້ອງການຍົກເລີກສິດ (Revoke) ຂອງຜູ້ໃຊ້ທີ່ເລືອກແທ້ຫຼືບໍ່?"

#: libraries/classes/Controllers/JavaScriptMessagesController.php:60
msgid "Do you really want to delete this central column?"
msgstr "ທ່ານຕ້ອງການລຶບຖັນຫຼັກນີ້ແທ້ຫຼືບໍ່?"

#: libraries/classes/Controllers/JavaScriptMessagesController.php:61
