#: libraries/classes/Engines/Myisam.php:26
msgid "Data pointer size"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດຂອງຕົວຊີ້ຂໍ້ມູນ (Data pointer size)"

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Myisam.php:28
msgid ""
"The default pointer size in bytes, to be used by CREATE TABLE for MyISAM "
"tables when no MAX_ROWS option is specified."
msgstr "ຂະໜາດຕົວຊີ້ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນເປັນໄບຕ໌."

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Myisam.php:34
msgid "Automatic recovery mode"
msgstr "ໂໝດກູ້ຄືນອັດຕະໂນມັດ"

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Myisam.php:36
msgid ""
"The mode for automatic recovery of crashed MyISAM tables, as set via the --"
"myisam-recover server startup option."
msgstr "ໂໝດການກູ້ຄືນອັດຕະໂນມັດສຳລັບຕາຕະລາງ MyISAM ທີ່ເສຍຫາຍ."

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Myisam.php:41
msgid "Maximum size for temporary sort files"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດສູງສຸດຂອງໄຟລ໌ຊົ່ວຄາວສຳລັບການຈັດລຽງ"

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Myisam.php:43
msgid ""
"The maximum size of the temporary file MySQL is allowed to use while re-"
"creating a MyISAM index (during REPAIR TABLE, ALTER TABLE, or LOAD DATA "
"INFILE)."
msgstr "ຂະໜາດສູງສຸດຂອງໄຟລ໌ຊົ່ວຄາວທີ່ MySQL ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ໃຊ້."

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Myisam.php:50
msgid "Maximum size for temporary files on index creation"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດສູງສຸດຂອງໄຟລ໌ຊົ່ວຄາວເມື່ອສ້າງອິນເດັກ"

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Myisam.php:52
msgid ""
"If the temporary file used for fast MyISAM index creation would be larger "
"than using the key cache by the amount specified here, prefer the key cache "
"method."
msgstr "ຫາກໄຟລ໌ຊົ່ວຄາວໃຫຍ່ກວ່າຄ່າທີ່ກຳນົດ, ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ວິທີ key cache ແທນ."

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Myisam.php:59
msgid "Repair threads"
msgstr "Thread ສຳລັບການຊ້ອມແຊມ"

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Myisam.php:61
msgid ""
"If this value is greater than 1, MyISAM table indexes are created in "
"parallel (each index in its own thread) during the repair by sorting process."
msgstr "ຫາກຄ່ານີ້ຫຼາຍກວ່າ 1, ອິນເດັກຂອງ MyISAM ຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນພ້ອມກັນ."

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Myisam.php:68
msgid "Sort buffer size"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດ Buffer ສຳລັບການຈັດລຽງ"

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Myisam.php:70
msgid ""
"The buffer that is allocated when sorting MyISAM indexes during a REPAIR "
"TABLE or when creating indexes with CREATE INDEX or ALTER TABLE."
msgstr "Buffer ທີ່ໃຊ້ໃນການຈັດລຽງອິນເດັກ MyISAM."

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:31
msgid "Index cache size"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດ Index cache"

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:33
msgid ""
"This is the amount of memory allocated to the index cache. Default value is "
"32MB. The memory allocated here is used only for caching index pages."
msgstr "ໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳທີ່ໃຊ້ສຳລັບ index cache. ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ 32MB."

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:40
msgid "Record cache size"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດ Record cache"

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:42
msgid ""
"This is the amount of memory allocated to the record cache used to cache "
"table data. The default value is 32MB. This memory is used to cache changes "
"to the handle data (.xtd) and row pointer (.xtr) files."
msgstr "ໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳທີ່ໃຊ້ສຳລັບ record cache. ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ 32MB."

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:50
msgid "Log cache size"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດ Log cache"

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:52
msgid ""
"The amount of memory allocated to the transaction log cache used to cache on "
"transaction log data. The default is 16MB."
msgstr "ໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳທີ່ໃຊ້ສຳລັບ transaction log cache. ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ 16MB."

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:59
msgid "Log file threshold"
msgstr "ຂີດຈຳກັດຂອງໄຟລ໌ລັອກ"

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:61
msgid ""
"The size of a transaction log before rollover, and a new log is created. The "
"default value is 16MB."
msgstr "ຂະໜາດຂອງ transaction log ກ່ອນທີ່ຈະສ້າງໄຟລ໌ໃໝ່. ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ 16MB."

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:67
msgid "Transaction buffer size"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດ Transaction buffer"

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:69
msgid ""
"The size of the global transaction log buffer (the engine allocates 2 "
"buffers of this size). The default is 1MB."
msgstr "ຂະໜາດຂອງ global transaction log buffer. ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ 1MB."

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:76
msgid "Checkpoint frequency"
msgstr "ຄວາມຖີ່ຂອງ Checkpoint"

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:78
msgid ""
"The amount of data written to the transaction log before a checkpoint is "
"performed. The default value is 24MB."
msgstr ""
"ຈຳນວນຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຂຽນລົງ transaction log ກ່ອນເຮັດ checkpoint. ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ 24MB."

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:85
msgid "Data log threshold"
msgstr "ຂີດຈຳກັດຂອງ Data log"

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:87
msgid ""
"The maximum size of a data log file. The default value is 64MB. PBXT can "
"create a maximum of 32000 data logs, which are used by all tables. So the "
"value of this variable can be increased to increase the total amount of data "
"that can be stored in the database."
msgstr "ຂະໜາດສູງສຸດຂອງໄຟລ໌ data log. ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ 64MB."

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:96
msgid "Garbage threshold"
msgstr "ຂີດຈຳກັດຂອງຂໍ້ມູນຂີ້ເຫຍື້ອ (Garbage threshold)"

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:98
msgid ""
"The percentage of garbage in a data log file before it is compacted. This is "
"a value between 1 and 99. The default is 50."
msgstr "ເປີເຊັນຂອງຂໍ້ມູນຂີ້ເຫຍື້ອກ່ອນທີ່ຈະຖືກບີບອັດ. ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ 50."

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:105
msgid "Log buffer size"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດ Log buffer"

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:107
msgid ""
"The size of the buffer used when writing a data log. The default is 256MB. "
"The engine allocates one buffer per thread, but only if the thread is "
"required to write a data log."
msgstr "ຂະໜາດຂອງ buffer ທີ່ໃຊ້ເມື່ອຂຽນ data log. ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ 256MB."

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:115
msgid "Data file grow size"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດການຂະຫຍາຍຂອງໄຟລ໌ຂໍ້ມູນ"

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:116
msgid "The grow size of the handle data (.xtd) files."
msgstr "ຂະໜາດການຂະຫຍາຍຂອງໄຟລ໌ (.xtd)."

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:120
msgid "Row file grow size"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດການຂະຫຍາຍຂອງໄຟລ໌ແຖວ"

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:121
msgid "The grow size of the row pointer (.xtr) files."
msgstr "ຂະໜາດການຂະຫຍາຍຂອງໄຟລ໌ (.xtr)."

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:125
msgid "Log file count"
msgstr "ຈຳນວນໄຟລ໌ລັອກ"

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:127
msgid ""
"This is the number of transaction log files (pbxt/system/xlog*.xt) the "
"system will maintain. If the number of logs exceeds this value then old logs "
"will be deleted, otherwise they are renamed and given the next highest "
"number."
msgstr "ຈຳນວນໄຟລ໌ transaction log ທີ່ລະບົບຈະເກັບໄວ້."

#: libraries/classes/Engines/Pbxt.php:185
#, possible-php-format
msgid ""
"Documentation and further information about PBXT can be found on the "
