#: libraries/classes/Normalization.php:335
msgid ""
"Do you have a group of columns which on combining gives an existing column? "
"For example, if you have first_name, last_name and full_name then combining "
"first_name and last_name gives full_name which is redundant."
msgstr ""
"ເຈົ້າມີກຸ່ມຄໍລຳທີ່ເມື່ອລວມກັນແລ້ວກາຍເປັນຄໍລຳທີ່ມີຢູ່ແລ້ວບໍ່? ຕົວຢ່າງ, ຖ້າເຈົ້າມີ first_name, last_name ແລ"
"ະ full_name, ການລວມ first_name ແລະ last_name ຈະໄດ້ full_name ເຊິ່ງຖືວ່າຊ້ຳຊ້ອນ."

#: libraries/classes/Normalization.php:341
