#: libraries/classes/Normalization.php:372
msgid ""
"Do you have a group of two or more columns that are closely related and are "
"all repeating the same attribute? For example, a table that holds data on "
"books might have columns such as book_id, author1, author2, author3 and so "
"on which form a repeating group. In this case a new table (book_id, author) "
"should be created."
msgstr ""
"ເຈົ້າມີກຸ່ມຂອງສອງຄໍລຳຂຶ້ນໄປທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັນຢ່າງໃກ້ຊິດ ແລະ ທັງໝົດເປັນຄຸນລັກສະນະດຽວກັນທີ່ຊ້ຳກັນບໍ່? ຕົວຢ່າງ, ຕາ"
"ຕະລາງທີ່ເກັບຂໍ້ມູນປຶ້ມອາດມີຄໍລຳເຊັ່ນ book_id, author1, author2, author3 ເຊິ່ງຖືວ່າເປັນກຸ່ມທີ່ຊ້ຳຄື"
"ນ. ໃນກໍລະນີນີ້ນີ້ ຄວນສ້າງຕາຕະລາງໃໝ່ (book_id, author)."

#: libraries/classes/Normalization.php:380
msgid ""
"Check the columns which form a repeating group. If no such group, click on "
"'No repeating group'"
msgstr ""
"ເລືອກຄໍລຳທີ່ເປັນກຸ່ມຊ້ຳຄືນ. ຖ້າບໍ່ມີກຸ່ມດັ່ງກ່າວ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກ 'ບໍ່ມີກຸ່ມຊ້ຳຄືນ'"

#: libraries/classes/Normalization.php:386
msgid "No repeating group"
msgstr "ບໍ່ມີກຸ່ມຊ້ຳຄືນ"

